<title>yạ sydy km kạn qạsyaⁿạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- yạ sydy km kạn qạsyaⁿ̃ạ mwt ṣlyb ạlʿạr
 wqbl ạ̉n yḥmlk ḥmlth yạ bạr
 1- sạ̉lt mạʾ dẖqt kẖlạaⁿ̃ dẖqt kl mrạr
 sạlt dmạk mn ḥsẖạk ltftdy ạlạsẖrạr
 2- fwq ạlṣlyb yạ ḥbyby km lqyt ậlạm
 mmn tmạdwạ fy ạ̹ydẖạk wkm gẖfrt ậtẖạm
 3- hl kl hdẖạ yạ ạ̹lhy ky tʿydny
 ạ̹ly̱ ḥmạk ạ̉ḥyạ mʿk wtʿzyny
 4- yạ lyt qlby ydnw mnk fạ̉fwz bk
 ạ̉ḥyạ lạ̉jlk ạ̉mynaⁿạ kẖạḍʿaⁿạ lk</lyrics>
